data.description: Discover the charm of this adorable home featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an attached 2-car garage. Nestled in a quiet community, this bright and spacious residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. The main floor welcomes you with a large living room, an inviting eat-in kitchen, a bathroom, two bedrooms, and convenient laundry facilities. Venture downstairs to find the third bedroom, a cozy family room, an additional bathroom, and a storage room offering ample space. Priced to sell
